Release Notes
This update improves the price label system and fixes a visual issue from the previous version.

Changes:
Fixed repeated price label issue that could display multiple labels across the chart
Optimized label handling so levels update instead of creating new labels each bar
Improved chart performance and visual clarity
Strategy logic and trading rules remain unchanged
This update focuses only on improving the visual behavior of price labels while keeping the core strategy identical.
